<HEADLINE>
<P>
ENTERTAINMENT CAREER DAY SET AT UCLA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 UCLA's Extension Entertainment Studies Department will have a career day in 
film, television and multimedia Aug. 20 from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Admission is free and no reservations are required. The workshop will be in 
100 Moore Hall. 
</P>
<P>
 UCLA Extension is also sponsoring a free open house for people considering a 
career in the music industry, Aug. 27, 10 a.m.-4 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: Department of Entertainment Studies and Performing Arts, 10995 Le 
Conte Ave., room 437, or call (310) 825-9064. 
</P>
