<TEXT>
<P>
 The exclusive Valley music charts are compiled for the Los Angeles Times from 
information supplied by SoundScan Inc., the music industry's leading 
sales-reporting service. The rankings are based on actual sales in the San 
Fernando, Santa Clarita and Antelope valleys and in Glendale. TOP 20 ALBUMS 
