<TEXT>
<P>
 * Roger F. Rodericks has been appointed vice president of AST Europe Ltd. for 
AST Research Inc., a personal computer manufacturer based in Irvine.Rodericks 
has been managing director of AST Europe Ltd. since 1990 and will continue in 
that role. The company said part of his focus as vice president will be to move 
AST into emerging Eastern European markets. Rodericks joined AST in 1984 as 
United Kingdom sales manager of its first overseas subsidiary. 
