<P>
 Baseball -- Umpire Bruce Froemming was incorrectly identified in Thursday's 
editions as the home plate umpire who ejected Dodger coach Reggie Smith from 
Wednesday night's game. The home plate umpire was Larry Poncino, and he made 
the ejection of Smith. 
</P>
